trans-unit.source: Enumerators provide read-only access to the data in the collection.
trans-unit.target: Enumeratorene gir skrivebeskyttet tilgang til dataene i samlingen.

trans-unit.source: Enumerators cannot be used to modify the underlying collection.
trans-unit.target: Enumeratorene kan ikke brukes til å endre den underliggende samlingen.

trans-unit.source: Initially, the enumerator is positioned before the first element in the collection.
trans-unit.target: I utgangspunktet er enumeratoren plassert før det første elementet i samlingen.

trans-unit.source: The <xref:System.Security.Cryptography.X509Certificates.X509Certificate2Enumerator.Reset%2A> method also brings the enumerator back to this position.
trans-unit.target: Den <xref:System.Security.Cryptography.X509Certificates.X509Certificate2Enumerator.Reset%2A>metoden henter også enumeratoren tilbake til denne plasseringen.</xref:System.Security.Cryptography.X509Certificates.X509Certificate2Enumerator.Reset%2A>

trans-unit.source: At this position, calling the <xref:System.Security.Cryptography.X509Certificates.X509Certificate2Enumerator.Current%2A> property throws an exception.
trans-unit.target: På dette Plasser, kaller den <xref:System.Security.Cryptography.X509Certificates.X509Certificate2Enumerator.Current%2A>egenskapen oppstår det et unntak.</xref:System.Security.Cryptography.X509Certificates.X509Certificate2Enumerator.Current%2A>

trans-unit.source: Therefore, you must call the <xref:System.Security.Cryptography.X509Certificates.X509Certificate2Enumerator.MoveNext%2A> method to advance the enumerator to the first element of the collection before reading the value of <xref:System.Security.Cryptography.X509Certificates.X509Certificate2Enumerator.Current%2A>.
trans-unit.target: Du må derfor kalle <xref:System.Security.Cryptography.X509Certificates.X509Certificate2Enumerator.MoveNext%2A>metoden for å gå videre enumeratoren til det første elementet i samlingen før leser <xref:System.Security.Cryptography.X509Certificates.X509Certificate2Enumerator.Current%2A>.</xref:System.Security.Cryptography.X509Certificates.X509Certificate2Enumerator.Current%2A> </xref:System.Security.Cryptography.X509Certificates.X509Certificate2Enumerator.MoveNext%2A>
